    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant damage, including deep scratches, several large dents, and noticeable rust patches on the wheel arches and undercarriage. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and some electronic components, such as the radio and interior lighting, are non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention due to a rough idle and a known transmission slip. We strongly advise a mechanical inspection before purchase, as it is not currently suitable for long-distance driving.",
