    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Distinguished by its mechanical integrity and professional upkeep, the automobile has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure optimal performance. It offers a sophisticated driving experience and exceptional value, standing as a testament to diligent ownership and consistent care.",
