    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hi everyone! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and I\u2019m honestly going to miss it. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super dependable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it\u2019s a smooth, comfy ride that\u2019s ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and it's just waiting for a new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
