      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a row-your-own 6-speed manual gearbox. It boasts sharp throttle response via individual throttle bodies and a predictable rear-end thanks to the M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive Vanos service and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the 8,000 RPM redline with poise. While the aesthetics show minor road-going patina consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains tight, providing the analog feedback and balanced dynamics that define this generation.",
